<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />
你每天都會確實早起，<delay8 />真是了不起呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道<delay8 />你有什麼訣竅嗎？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！<delay20 />沒有啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我這樣很普通啊！<delay frames="30" />
不過我習慣會<delay8 />早睡就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難就難在你說的普通啊～<delay frames="30" />
要我認真地乖乖起床，我實在辦不到哩～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒有其他<delay20 />能更輕鬆<delay8 />
又更快的方法嗎？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />這個嘛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<20_3 arg="6" />你有什麼好點子嗎？</message>
	<message label="004_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">早一點睡</message>
	<message label="004_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">早起做事</message>
	<message label="004_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">整晚不睡</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />說的也對！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然還是只能這樣呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼～！<delay frames="30" />
果然還是得這樣嗎？<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay20 />你們兩個都好認真啊～<delay frames="30" />
<20_2 arg="7" />不過這也是<delay8 />
你們的優點啦！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你辦得到的，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="5" /><delay20 /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在你養成早睡早起的習慣前，<delay20 />
我會負起責任<delay8 />協助你的！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就<delay20 />不必了啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />那方法不錯耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早上如果能有件令人期待的事，<delay20 />
感覺不管多早都爬得起來呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay8 />既然如此<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<20_2 arg="7" />那就讀本書，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />或是做運動之類的，
你覺得怎麼樣？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來如此啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到看書，<delay20 />我家裡還有
買了都還沒看過的書呢～<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><delay20 />一回想起來，就突然好想看！<delay frames="30" /><20_2 arg="8" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～<delay20 />我要來讀那本書啦！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="7" />你可別看得太著迷，<delay20 />
就熬夜看一整晚喔！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
想不到你還滿淘氣的呢，<delay frames="30" />
竟然會說這種玩笑話<20_3 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對喔！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />整晚不睡不就起得來了嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你真是天才耶！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" />如果是這樣，感覺我也辦得到！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就從今晚<delay8 />開始試試看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別、<delay20 />別把玩笑話當真啦，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡以前<delay8 />真不愧是座無人島，<delay20 />
到處都綠意盎然耶～！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是說呢！<delay frames="30" />
可以看到各式各樣的花朵，<delay20 />
我覺得<delay8 />好開心！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對啊～！<delay frames="40" />
而且還有我沒種過的花，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真讓我躍躍欲試哩！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
你真的很喜歡花呢！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很喜歡<delay8 />用花來裝飾房間喔！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />家裡只要裝飾了花，<delay8 />空間就會明亮起來！<10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />看著這座島上的花……<delay20 />
就會覺得維持它們原本自然的樣子也不錯哩。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂你說的！<10_4 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />陽光照射在花上的時候，<delay8 />實在太美了，<delay20 />
不管看多久都不會膩呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過如果一直在外面看花的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會很介意昆蟲就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你討厭昆蟲，<delay20 />
可是沒辦法在這種小島上生活的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過沒關係，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在你習慣昆蟲之前，<delay8 />
我會幫你想辦法的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以有什麼狀況就告訴我吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay8 />
總覺得你好帥氣喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />總之，大概就是像這樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我才得以救出我的手下<tag a="110" b="0" />
不對，<delay20 />我是說死黨啦！</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay8 />好厲害喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種事情我實在學不來！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，你好有力量，<delay20 />
讓我有點羨慕呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個，<delay20 />就算只是說話方式也好，
我可以試著模仿你一下嗎？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不要吧，<delay20 />我的說話方式不適合你，
你還是死心吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那樣的話，<delay20 />請至少讓我用用
你的那句「<tag a="110" b="5" />」吧！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Apologize" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜託你！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是可以，<delay20 />這倒無所謂啦<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的嗎！？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～！<delay frames="30" />
真是謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我還是覺得<delay8 />
你照你原本的樣子就行了啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>